  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a Muscle Obstacle Cource VR game. <br>Become a challenger of the muscle TV show \"Muscle Ninja\" and conquer all levels! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Goal of the game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/0045fa31dcf8c3546619ff9598c7b234.avif?t=1730128469\" width=580 height=162 /></span>The levels of \"Muscle Ninja\" consist of multiple areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal of the game is to clear the stage by overcoming the gimmicks in each area and pressing the goal button within the time limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/2efcca96f80f6c1e53c753f0c2a4cf1e.poster.avif?t=1730128469\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/2efcca96f80f6c1e53c753f0c2a4cf1e.webm?t=1730128469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/2efcca96f80f6c1e53c753f0c2a4cf1e.mp4?t=1730128469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab a handrail or wall with VR controller grip and pull to move forward. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The intuitive operation is just like actually climbing up a wall, making it possible to have a realistic VR experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/ff558a928b4392de0cbfaa02585a713a.poster.avif?t=1730128469\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/ff558a928b4392de0cbfaa02585a713a.webm?t=1730128469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/ff558a928b4392de0cbfaa02585a713a.mp4?t=1730128469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, if your hand slips, you will fall headlong!　The fear of falling is also unique to VR!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Live commentary</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live commentary enhances the game play.<br>Live audio is available in Japanese and English.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Subtitles are available in all languages, and can be displayed on both the HMD and the streaming screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with your favorite avatar! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/af113e5855269336fefac1584adc9065.avif?t=1730128469\" width=580 height=250 /></span>You You can use VRM format model files as player avatars. <br>The game includes bundled avatars so you can play without your own one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sstream it! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/4d9c5ab759e7d27752624b72b914e125.avif?t=1730128469\" width=600 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A “Streaming Screen” from a third-person perspective view is displayed on your PC monitor.<br>Let your friends and fans watch your playing!<br>Of course, HMD mirroring can also be displayed.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Variety of difficulty options</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the high difficulty “Full Real Mode” you must clear all stages without falling once.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will feel a great sense of accomplishment from the tension of not being allowed to make a mistake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Enjoy Mode” is for those who want to enjoy the game casually. Long time limit and checkpoint retry make it possible to play with peace of mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About secondary use </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We fully permit the posting and streaming of images and video using the play screen and audio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Supported Platforms</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This title is exclusive to Steam VR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Steam VR compatible VR headset is required to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are currently no plans to release this game outside of Steam.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a Muscle Obstacle Cource VR game. <br>Become a challenger of the muscle TV show \"Muscle Ninja\" and conquer all levels! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Goal of the game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/0045fa31dcf8c3546619ff9598c7b234.avif?t=1730128469\" width=580 height=162 /></span>The levels of \"Muscle Ninja\" consist of multiple areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal of the game is to clear the stage by overcoming the gimmicks in each area and pressing the goal button within the time limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/2efcca96f80f6c1e53c753f0c2a4cf1e.poster.avif?t=1730128469\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/2efcca96f80f6c1e53c753f0c2a4cf1e.webm?t=1730128469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/2efcca96f80f6c1e53c753f0c2a4cf1e.mp4?t=1730128469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab a handrail or wall with VR controller grip and pull to move forward. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The intuitive operation is just like actually climbing up a wall, making it possible to have a realistic VR experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/ff558a928b4392de0cbfaa02585a713a.poster.avif?t=1730128469\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/ff558a928b4392de0cbfaa02585a713a.webm?t=1730128469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/ff558a928b4392de0cbfaa02585a713a.mp4?t=1730128469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, if your hand slips, you will fall headlong!　The fear of falling is also unique to VR!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Live commentary</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live commentary enhances the game play.<br>Live audio is available in Japanese and English.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Subtitles are available in all languages, and can be displayed on both the HMD and the streaming screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with your favorite avatar! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/af113e5855269336fefac1584adc9065.avif?t=1730128469\" width=580 height=250 /></span>You You can use VRM format model files as player avatars. <br>The game includes bundled avatars so you can play without your own one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sstream it! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552600/extras/4d9c5ab759e7d27752624b72b914e125.avif?t=1730128469\" width=600 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A “Streaming Screen” from a third-person perspective view is displayed on your PC monitor.<br>Let your friends and fans watch your playing!<br>Of course, HMD mirroring can also be displayed.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Variety of difficulty options</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the high difficulty “Full Real Mode” you must clear all stages without falling once.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will feel a great sense of accomplishment from the tension of not being allowed to make a mistake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Enjoy Mode” is for those who want to enjoy the game casually. Long time limit and checkpoint retry make it possible to play with peace of mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About secondary use </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We fully permit the posting and streaming of images and video using the play screen and audio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Supported Platforms</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This title is exclusive to Steam VR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Steam VR compatible VR headset is required to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are currently no plans to release this game outside of Steam.</p>",
